@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Identity
@inject SignInManager<IdentityUser> SignInManager
@inject UserManager<IdentityUser> UserManager
<ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
    @if (SignInManager.IsSignedIn(User))
    {
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a id="manage" class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="Identity"
               asp-page="/Account/Manage/Index" title="Manage">
                Hello @UserManager.GetUserName(User)!
            </a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
            <form id="logoutForm" class="form-inline" asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Logout" asp-route-returnUrl="@Url.Action( "Index", "Home" , new { area="" })">
                <button id="logout" type="submit" class="nav-link btn btn-link text-dark" style="padding:15px 10px;color:red">
                    退出
                </button>
            </form>
        </li>
    }
    else
    {
        
            <li class="nav-item" style="font-size:18px">
                <a class="nav-link text-dark" id="register"
                   asp-area="Identity"
                   asp-page="/Account/Register">注册</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item" style="font-size:18px">
                <a class="nav-link text-dark" id="login"
                   asp-area="Identity"
                   asp-page="/Account/Login">登录</a>
            </li>
       
    }
</ul>

<script type="text/javascript">
    // script.js
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
        var link = document.getElementById('login');
        var currentUrl = window.location.href;

        if (currentUrl.includes('Login')) {
            link.classList.remove('nav-link-style1');
            link.classList.add('nav-link-style2');
        } else if (currentUrl.includes('Register')) {
            link.classList.remove('nav-link-style2');
            link.classList.add('nav-link-style1');
        }
        
    });
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
        var link = document.getElementById('register');
        var currentUrl = window.location.href;
        if (currentUrl.includes('Login')) {
            link.classList.remove('nav-link-style2');
            link.classList.add('nav-link-style1');
        } else if (currentUrl.includes('Register')) {
            link.classList.remove('nav-link-style1');
            link.classList.add('nav-link-style2');
        }
    });

</script>